 providing relief of hyperacidity symptoms. [PharmGKB]', 'Intravenous sodium bicarbonate therapy increases plasma bicarbonate, buffers excess hydrogen ion concentration, raises blood pH and reverses the clinical manifestations of acidosis.', 'DrugBank', 0, 0, 0);
